snippet.title: State of Anarchy: Master of Mayhem - new trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/576130/State_of_Anarchy_Complete_Master_of_Mayhem/
Simplistic shooter that will put a smile on your face. Your town is on fire, anarchy reigns the streets, aliens rampage in the sky! Grab your gun and join the fun!
State of Anarchy: Master of Mayhem is available on Nintendo Switch™, Xbox One and PlayStation 4:
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/state-of-anarchy-master-of-mayhem-switch
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/state-of-anarchy-master-of-mayhem/bp8f95f6nvhm
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP1675-CUSA11816_00-SYPS4STATEOFANAR
